  "body": "<!-- Please only use this template for submitting enhancement requests -->\r\n\r\n**What would you like to be added**:\r\n\r\nI want to create HPA instances via `kubectl autoscale` for our custom controllers which implement the scale subresource, so that I can run\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n$ kubectl autoscale vmirs vmi-replicaset-cirros --min=2 --max=5\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Why is this needed**:\r\n\r\nWe are implementing the scale subresource for our CRDs and I can create HPA instances for our controller instances via the declarative workflow (`kubectl create`). However, if I try to create it via `kubectl autoscale`, I get:\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n$ kubectl autoscale vmirs vmi-replicaset-cirros --min=2 --max=5\r\nerror: no kind \"VirtualMachineInstanceReplicaSet\" is registered for version \"kubevirt.io/v1alpha2\"\r\n```\r\nIt will make HPA usage for custom controllers more accessible for the imperative workflows.",
